@startuml REQ-PROD-003 Over-the-Air Firmware Update
autonumber

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
  participant "OTA Manager" as OTA_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-PROD-003: Over-the-Air Firmware Update**
  //Description:// The system shall support remote firmware updates with integrity verification
  //Acceptance Criteria:// OTA completes download/flash/verify cycle; device reports success or failure to cloud
  //Preconditions:// REQ-0020 (Remote Status Reporting)
end header


Comm_Manager --> OTA_Manager: EVENT:COMM_CHUNK_RECEIVED\nComm_DownloadFirmware() → OTA_OnChunkReceived()
Comm_Manager --> OTA_Manager: EVENT:COMM_DOWNLOAD_COMPLETE\nComm_DownloadFirmware() → OTA_OnDownloadComplete()
OTA_Manager --> Comm_Manager: EVENT:COMM_DOWNLOAD_START\nOTA_OnUpdateAvailable() → Comm_DownloadFirmware()
note right of OTA_Manager: OTA_STATE_CHANGE

@enduml